<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8345366>
    dc:description "FIGURES 75–81. Lomechusoides folgaricus sp. nov. 75, male paratype, dorsal habitus; 76–80, male holotype; (locality: Italy, Folgaria, Tirolis). 76, pronotum in dorsal view (L: 1.15 mm, W: 1.75 mm); 77, aedeagus, lateral view; 78, aedeagus, ventral view; 79, metaventral process; 80, apex of paramere; 81, female paratype, spermatheca, (locality: Italy, Folgaria, Tirolis). Scale bars in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8345366/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

